reviewText: It's a decent course if you are a complete beginner to Excel, however, it's listed as an intermediate level course. There is nothing really indicating this course is at that intermediate level. The topics are too simple and linear. However, the instructor was good at explaining each step and going at a reasonable pace which to a novice is perfect to begin with.
